## Color and Background
#### Use 'color' to set text color and  'background' for background color
```

<html>
<!--在这里插入内容-->
body{
    background: #
    color: #
    background: url() // will repeat image if it is not big enough.
    background-repeat: no-repeat; // wont repeat the image, may cause blank left
    background-size:cover; //strech the image to cover the body
}
</html>

```

## Border:
#### 3 property:
```

<html>
<!--在这里插入内容-->
- border-color: purple;
- border-width: 2px;
- border-style: solid; 
</html>
```

shortcuts:
border: 5px solid purple;
